    public abstract static class AnimatedExpandableListView.AnimatedExpandableListAdapter
extends android.widget.BaseExpandableListAdapter
    A specialized adapter for use with the AnimatedExpandableListView. All adapters used with AnimatedExpandableListView MUST extend this class.
